name: Go Home (JafCraze)
description:
Monsters incoming - Send them packing Warning: This game was rushed. Expect some bugs!
Press space as soon as the game loads
If the game freezes or it's game over, refresh the page

Arrows Keys / WASD / ZQSD to direct the monsters to their home

Can you beat 130?

Made for TriJam #108
Theme: Creepy vibes
